p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal
	{margin:0in;
	margin-bottom:.0001pt;
	font-size:12.0pt;
	font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";}

	{mso-style-priority:99;
	color:blue;
	text-decoration:underline;}

	{mso-style-priority:99;
	color:purple;
	text-decoration:underline;}

	{mso-style-priority:99;
	mso-margin-top-alt:auto;
	margin-right:0in;
	mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
	margin-left:0in;
	font-size:12.0pt;
	font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";}

	margin-right:12.0pt;
	mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
	margin-left:12.0pt;
	font-size:12.0pt;
	font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";}
